column5: If specified, @BinderySignatureIDs SHALL list the BinderySignature/ @BinderySignatureID of all BinderySignatures that are processed by this Station.
If present, @ShapeDefRef SHALL reference a ShapeDef that defines the shape of the Station in the DieLayout.
The name of the 1-up design in the DieLayout. Multiple stations with the same @StationName MAY be specified.
